      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">老子 81.1 - 老子 81.3</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">老子 81.1 - 老子 81.3</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>信言不美，美言不信。善者不辯，</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>Sincere words are not fine; fine words are not sincere. Those who are skilled (in the Dao) do not dispute (about it);</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
